This directory contains various contributed files for Inform:

    inform-mode.el	A GNU Emacs Inform mode, contributed by
			Gareth Rees <Gareth.Rees@cl.cam.ac.uk>, and
			currently maintained by Rupert Lane
			<rupert@merguez.demon.co.uk>.

    pblorb.pl		Generate a blorb file according to a supplied
			blurb file.  Originally by Graham Nelson.
			Currently maintained by David Griffith.

    scanblorb.pl	Reads a Blorb interactive fiction resource file,
			checks for validity, and reports on its
			contents. The contents of the Blorb file can also
			be extracted to individual files.
			Originally by Graham Nelson.  Currently
			maintained by David Griffith.
